Firmware licensing
==================

The firmware and configuration blobs in this directory
(e.g. Marvell and MediaTek) are not covered by the
GNU General Public License.

These files are binary firmware provided by hardware vendors and
are distributed under their respective licenses.

Where available, license information is taken from the upstream
linux-firmware repository:
https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/firmware/linux-firmware.git

In cases where no explicit license file is present, the firmware
is assumed to be redistributable, but may not permit modification.

===================

For the firmware under mrvl/ (currently empty), see LICENCE.Marvell

===================

For the firmware under mediatek/ (currently empty), see LICENCE.mediatek


For the MediaTek 7668 firmware and cfg files under ./
licensing terms are provided by the original vendor (MediaTek)
and are typically "redistributable firmware" licenses.

Please inquire the original repository by Khadas and ZTE
https://github.com/khadas/android_hardware_wifi_mtk_drivers_mt7668/
for the proper licensing, though it is not likely far off from
LICENCE.mediatek.


